{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"40":{"eng-name":"Prescribed Punishments (Kitab Al-Hudud)","ara-name":"كتاب الحدود"}},"section_detail":{"40":{"hadithnumber_first":4351,"hadithnumber_last":4493,"arabicnumber_first":4351,"arabicnumber_last":4493}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":4433,"arabicnumber":4433,"text":"حَدَّثَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ أَبِي بَكْرِ بْنِ أَبِي شَيْبَةَ، حَدَّثَنَا يَحْيَى بْنُ يَعْلَى بْنِ الْحَارِثِ، حَدَّثَنَا أَبِي، عَنْ غَيْلاَنَ، عَنْ عَلْقَمَةَ بْنِ مَرْثَدٍ، عَنِ ابْنِ بُرَيْدَةَ، عَنْ أَبِيهِ، أَنَّ النَّبِيَّ صلى الله عليه وسلم اسْتَنْكَهَ مَاعِزًا ‏.‏","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Muslim (1695)"}],"reference":{"book":40,"hadith":83},"chapter":{"id":24,"ara-name":"باب رَجْمِ مَاعِزِ بْنِ مَالِكٍ","eng-name":"Stoning of Ma'iz bin Malik","isFirstHadith":false}}]}